# Cloudflare Pages headers.
# Cross-origin isolation enables multi-threaded WASM (SharedArrayBuffer) for the
# WebGPU/WASM Whisper engine. `credentialless` lets us still fetch models from a
# cross-origin CDN (e.g. Hugging Face) without them needing CORP headers.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless

# Vite fingerprints asset filenames, so they're safe to cache forever.
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
